{"type": "article", "id": 30741, "title": "鼓励职场互动的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-08T23:00:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160808180634lBTXkmap7eUi09IV.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>你还记得那个用来鼓励同事之间进行交流的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30542.html\">花盆系统</a>吗？这个需要两个人共同参与操作的灯具 A Play Of Dependencies 有着异曲同工之妙：灯具的两端含有磁性，由于中间的电力回路受到阻断，需要安装上木头与黄铜制成的连接器才能使电路接通。设计师 <a href=\"http://www.mayapindeus.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maya Pindeus</a> 和 Johanna Pichlbauer 希望通过这个需要动手组装的设计将人与人之间的互动带回职场。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608081806561n4K5uBITXh0opGr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808180656qOJkes47RArXi8YT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808180656IeE6PK2CvB5dj4Xb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808180656ETmFutMdC9BGp7HA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}